   <concept id="FAR_22_810" class="- topic/topic concept/concept " xtrc="">
      <title class="- topic/title ">
         <ph class="- topic/ph " props="autonumber">22.810</ph> Solicitation provisions and contract clauses.</title>
      <conbody class="- topic/body concept/conbody ">
         <ol id="d1359e13" class="- topic/ol ">
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p class="- topic/p " id="d1395e10">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(a)</ph>
						            When a contract is contemplated that will include the clause at <xref href="52.222-26.dita#FAR_52_222_26"
                        base="i1055793"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref "/>, Equal Opportunity, the contracting officer shall insert-</p>
               <ol id="d1359e26" class="- topic/ol ">
                  <li class="- topic/li ">
                     <p class="- topic/p " id="d1395e19">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(1)</ph>
								                The clause at <xref href="52.222-21.dita#FAR_52_222_21"
                              base="i1055713"
                              outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                              class="- topic/xref "/>, Prohibition of Segregated Facilities, in the solicitation and contract; and</p>
                  </li>
                  <li class="- topic/li ">
                     <p class="- topic/p " id="d1395e27">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(2)</ph>
								                The provision at <xref href="52.222-22.dita#FAR_52_222_22"
                              base="i1055729"
                              outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                              class="- topic/xref "/>, Previous Contracts and Compliance Reports, in the solicitation.</p>
                  </li>
               </ol>
            </li>
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p class="- topic/p " id="d1395e35">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(b)</ph>
						            The contracting officer shall insert the provision at <xref href="52.222-23.dita#FAR_52_222_23"
                        base="i1055741"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref "/>, Notice of Requirement for Affirmative Action to Ensure Equal Employment Opportunity for Construction, in solicitations for construction when a contract is contemplated that will include the clause at <xref href="52.222-26.dita#FAR_52_222_26"
                        base="i1055793"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref "/>, Equal Opportunity, and the amount of the contract is expected to be in excess of $10,000.</p>
            </li>
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p class="- topic/p " id="d1395e46">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(c)</ph>
						            The contracting officer shall insert the provision at <xref href="52.222-24.dita#FAR_52_222_24"
                        base="i1055773"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref "/>, Preaward On-Site Equal Opportunity Compliance Evaluation, in solicitations other than those for construction when a contract is contemplated that will include the clause at <xref href="52.222-26.dita#FAR_52_222_26"
                        base="i1055793"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref "/>, Equal Opportunity, and the amount of the contract is expected be $10 million or more.</p>
            </li>
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p class="- topic/p " id="d1395e57">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(d)</ph>
						            The contracting officer shall insert the provision at <xref href="52.222-25.dita#FAR_52_222_25"
                        base="i1055782"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref "/>, Affirmative Action Compliance, in solicitations, other than those for construction, when a contract is contemplated that will include the clause at <xref href="52.222-26.dita#FAR_52_222_26"
                        base="i1055793"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref "/>, Equal Opportunity.</p>
            </li>
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p class="- topic/p " id="d1395e68">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(e)</ph>
						            The contracting officer shall insert the clause at <xref href="52.222-26.dita#FAR_52_222_26"
                        base="i1055793"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref "/>, Equal Opportunity, in solicitations and contracts (see <xref href="22.802.dita#FAR_22_802"
                        base="i1097248"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">22.802</xref>) unless the contract is exempt from all of the requirements of E.O.11246 (see <xref href="22.807.dita#FAR_22_807"
                        base="i1097315"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">22.807</xref>(a)). If the contract is exempt from one or more, but not all, of the requirements of E.O.11246, the contracting officer shall use the clause with its Alternate I.</p>
            </li>
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p class="- topic/p " id="d1395e82">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(f)</ph>
						            The contracting officer shall insert the clause at <xref href="52.222-27.dita#FAR_52_222_27"
                        base="i1055834"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref "/>, Affirmative Action Compliance Requirements for Construction, in solicitations and contracts for construction that will include the clause at <xref href="52.222-26.dita#FAR_52_222_26"
                        base="i1055793"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref "/>, Equal Opportunity, when the amount of the contract is expected to be in excess of $10,000.</p>
            </li>
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p class="- topic/p " id="d1395e93">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(g)</ph>
						            The contracting officer shall insert the clause at <xref href="52.222-29.dita#FAR_52_222_29"
                        base="i1055899"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref "/>, Notification of Visa Denial, in contracts that will include the clause at <xref href="52.222-26.dita#FAR_52_222_26"
                        base="i1055793"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref "/>, Equal Opportunity, if the contractor is required to perform in or on behalf of a foreign country.</p>
            </li>
         </ol>
      </conbody>
   </concept>
